T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-21 12:42am-10:42pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sWB4nSk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsWB4nSk.png&h=41d50bef&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/my4USGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fmy4USGM.png&h=ac71398e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(13)彭慧中vs陳嘉寶(6)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"7ff53d4142e95cad33b874397c19ba35983b30fa","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":64,"dislike":59,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-21 12:44am-10:44pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/007iIPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F007iIPg.png&h=c3ed5227&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZFz9SGc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZFz9SGc.png&h=2d03ff95&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(17)劉佩玥vs簡幗儀(15)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"589c21f3663c4968ef70a1bbc9a39955eb5dd94e","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"最後兩輪冠軍聯賽賽程:<br />\n<br />\n33.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-05<br />\n沈卓盈v黃翠如<br />\n鄧麗欣v劉佩玥<br />\n麥美恩v林泳淘<br />\n陳嘉寶v莊錠欣<br />\n文詠珊v彭慧中<br />\n陳煒v簡幗儀<br />\n孫慧雪v黃心美<br />\n黃心穎v岑麗香<br />\n袁澧林v陳法拉<br />\n<br />\n34.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-12<br />\n黃心美v陳嘉寶<br />\n彭慧中v黃心穎<br />\n岑麗香v鄧麗欣<br />\n陳法拉v麥美恩<br />\n劉佩玥v孫慧雪<br />\n莊錠欣v沈卓盈<br />\n簡幗儀v袁澧林<br />\n黃翠如v文詠珊<br />\n林泳淘v陳煒"},{"pid":"0a0a4e9d1d426656928671d97d1133863f709d9e","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":96,"dislike":38,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-21 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sym9mKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fsym9mKC.png&h=7fc067ad&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EHEZ1xx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEHEZ1xx.png&h=4d03d4c0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(1)文詠珊vs沈卓盈(3)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"35e0bace5f2ad707c6c723073532db0af276053b","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃決賽會係4月29日舉行<br />\n文詠珊VS李佳芯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/636206/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/636206/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強已經誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新垣結衣(日本)<br />\nvs<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE(台灣)<br />\n<br />\nIU(韓國)<br />\nvs<br />\n謝安琪(香港)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽籤將於下星期舉行,有結果會再另行公佈<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3de3b07f475e1c303c722604bd7a7cedd797b","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77188b58605c97a8ac5be257414415eca6dacfaa","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87bcd8b760e3b175a84208928ba65249fe98698","tid":636263,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335d3d10986117d5f439bb4bb490ecf633745f90","tid":636263,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r